{"tid":434251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★又來了！IT界難請人　求才若渴起薪點可達2萬元","createTime":"2017-10-13T06:05:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-13T12:33:13.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"54973227e8a4c8641e25de0b42e7e02be95dbc6d","tid":434251,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T06:05:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2個空缺要半年先請到人</span><br />\n<br />\n「我哋就係好想請呢類人才，可惜佢（陳奕希）已經有其他公司請咗。」資訊科技公司先達智能負責人Jackei Wong表示，現時資訊科技（IT）界缺人情況嚴重，中小企很難聘請合適的人才，原因在於就讀相關科目的學生即使尚未畢業，已有2至3間公司向其招手，因而有很多選擇：「曾經試過有2個空缺，要半年時間先請得到&hellip;&hellip;依家係學生揀工，唔係工揀佢，好難請到有經驗、眼界闊嘅學生，可以話係求才若渴。」<br />\n<br />\n在薪酬待遇方面，Jackei表示，一般畢業生的起薪點可達1.5萬元，如具一定經驗或擁有優秀能力的畢業生，起薪點可達2萬元；對此，陳奕希透露，其月薪已接近2萬元。<br />\n<br />\n晉升階梯明確<br />\n<br />\n在晉升前景方面，Jackei則指出，畢業生在初入職2年內，主要負責開發工作，向僱主證明自己的能力；在2年後，需開始自行面對客戶，與對方溝通；3年後，可開始建立4至5人的小團隊，專責進行項目開發；當擁有5至6年經驗，並擁有足夠實戰經驗、穩定基礎後，則可升至經理級別。<br />\n<br />\nJackei又表示作為僱主，亦十分希望可聘請具比賽經驗的學生或畢業生，他解釋：「返工都要有心理質素，經常會有趕deadline（死線）壓力。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/123732/thumbnail/5c6d2f81fcdfcf63ed472a1c4622c82b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F123732%2Fthumbnail%2F5c6d2f81fcdfcf63ed472a1c4622c82b.jpg&h=de8b4239&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/港聞/123732/IT界難請人-求才若渴起薪點可達2萬元-6年可升至經理級\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2F123732%2FIT%E7%95%8C%E9%9B%A3%E8%AB%8B%E4%BA%BA-%E6%B1%82%E6%89%8D%E8%8B%A5%E6%B8%B4%E8%B5%B7%E8%96%AA%E9%BB%9E%E5%8F%AF%E9%81%942%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83-6%E5%B9%B4%E5%8F%AF%E5%8D%87%E8%87%B3%E7%B6%93%E7%90%86%E7%B4%9A&d=qnyDmDJSuYoO2CgVZiaTeP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=17676a42\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/港聞/123732/IT界難請人-求才若渴起薪點可達2萬元-6年可升至經理級</a>"},{"pid":"85b51d626e54733f96965c4531cce3e7586e7deb","tid":434251,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T06:05:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43448f86d8af4ea456b391a1d52ba02e4229708f","tid":434251,"uid":65778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T06:06:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c1e4605e8e95a5138db93ea8a102981375253f9","tid":434251,"uid":146604,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T06:07:21.000Z","msg":"洗碗都兩萬 仲包埋膳食 IT狗算什麼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cff9f747d5ee0955bcd06ed5c7494e40f6583a82","tid":434251,"uid":90,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T06:08:30.000Z","msg":"It係非常有前途的！<br />\nIt=搵錢科<br />\nIt=發達"},{"pid":"1f4f722f4c189306cc06781eccfa8a026d53f7a7","tid":434251,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T06:08:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>洗碗都兩萬 仲包埋膳食 IT狗算什麼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔夠睇醫生"},{"pid":"c6514e8eab21f2866741cea254fe1a66539cfc2a","tid":434251,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T06:09:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>It係非常有前途的！<br />\nIt=搵錢科<br />\nIt=發達</blockquote><br />\nu are<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67569a295698da1c73a020be2a0c5a0cca7b20