es/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔做it就傻仔喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nibank?</blockquote><br />\n細公司support<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n細公司support 有32k <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\nKeep住做！有前途呀你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c94173b4994235ce8f14f77151b674c587e6e69","tid":434251,"uid":48022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T10:57:02.000Z","msg":"政府請AP2 Pt. 16 ~ 27"},{"pid":"47ceea90a0ee4c43fdd0d8e6f34e568785fe4350","tid":434251,"uid":48022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T10:58:08.000Z","msg":"政府請AP2 Pt. 16 ~ 27"},{"pid":"99f7b238bb2c9fbae64519202b5420c5c7ebb85d","tid":434251,"uid":7760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T11:05:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>根據觀察，樓豬炒股唔得，買就跌唔買就升，車津冇份老綜冇加，水貨唔願做，各種打擊令佢變成憤世廢老，要搵佢老友蓋清開導佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呼喚蓋清 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nno<br />\n蓋青is<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n蓋清為你好咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓豬乜都唔願做<br />\n嫌依樣嫌果樣"},{"pid":"c3a0604b75164f5394391fcd4d5ca8adc370e139","tid":434251,"uid":84436,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T11:07:51.000Z","msg":"每天的循環<br />\n<br />\n睇到 大公司一堆裁員消息  \t就知道春天到了 \t,炒中年IT人準備請新人<br />\n<br />\n睇到 新聞壓價IT畢業生消息 \t就知道夏天到了\t,壓價吸新人<br />\n<br />\n睇到 請人難IT畢業生有前景 \t就知道秋天到了\t,引D中低下層學生讀"},{"pid":"1ef4eb783ca6dd2ce6afb4f8a9cf109d95e80968","tid":434251,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T11:08:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每天的循環<br />\n<br />\n睇到 大公司一堆裁員消息  \t就知道春天到了 \t,炒中年IT人準備請新人<br />\n<br />\n睇到 新聞壓價IT畢業生消息 \t就知道夏天到了\t,壓價吸新人<br />\n<br />\n睇到 請人難IT畢業生有前景 \t就知道秋天到了\t,引D中低下層學生讀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n每<span style=\"color: red;\">年</span>的循環<br />\n<br />\n睇到 大公司一堆裁員消息  \t就知道春天到了 \t,炒中年IT人準備請新人<br />\n<br />\n睇到 新聞壓價IT畢業生消息 \t就知道夏天到了\t,壓價吸新人<br />\n<br />\n睇到 請人難IT畢業生有前景 \t就知道秋天到了\t,引D中低下層學生讀"},{"pid":"e67a5f461abedaf2be2cd586ada45cbdb6e630d4","tid":434251,"uid":84436,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T11:16:15.000Z","msg":"畢業時  ACO(政府工既文員-助理文書主任) IT(support,infra,si,coder)<br />\nACO: 起薪近15K <br />\nIT\t:IVE/UGRAD 平均12-17K 左近<br />\n<br />\nACO: 每日一般6點前走人,很少OT,OT好似都可以報,放工唔洗諗公司野<br />\nIT\t:每日一般7-8點左右走人,常常OT,仲要晚上隨時收call support,check email<br />\n<br />\n到40中<br />\nACO :升上CO(pt16-21), CO人工近40K(40K係未計通脹 每年再加幾%),工作如常 幾年換一次位, 好似22日假,強積金供出面好多,又可以申請公屋居屋,不用擔心住屋醫療<br />\nIT人 :通常都係40K左右 ,工作如常 OTOT, IT人多數合約工 好少福利...開始outdated,跟唔上後生, 除時被炒又搵工,租屋比較安全<br />\n<br />\n到50中<br />\nCO好運升上SCO人工50K左右(未計通脹 每年再加幾%),安守本份,不會比人炒,等到65歲退休.福利照舊 不怕經濟起伏<br />\nIT人,晉升不明朗,可能經過被炒N次 已轉行,人工變動好大,可能都係落手落腳前線位 ,少數可能上到管理職位<br />\n<br />\n到65歲<br />\nCO/SCO :光榮退休 服務政府大眾40年,有好既退休保障<br />\nIT :不知道<br />\n<br />\nACO睇落普普通通 但做左20年既人到中年後一般都會有40-50K(計埋通脤)<br />\n1.唔會怕中年失業,可以keep住升職and加人工<br />\n2.可以住緊用公務員隊申請既公屋, 唔洗煩住屋問題 <br />\n3.有2X日假,請假又唔難批<br />\n4.每月有2X%強積金幫你供 <br />\n5.朝9晚6少OT,就算要OT都可似claim返 <br />\n6.唔洗擦鞋保住份工,有理既可以話返上司轉頭<br />\n7.放工唔洗keep住進修,怕比後生取代<br />\n8.work life balance,放工就放工去邊玩,照顧屋企人就得唔會比工作搞到冇曬私人時間<br />\n9.幾年換一次位,有好有唔好,但唔洗一世做同一個位同一樣野<br />\n<br />\n2A3O officer , EO ,紀律部隊更加比做IT 有前途<br />\npoint 22 以上好似仲可以申請供樓資助,約10年 每月有幾K 置 1X K<br />\n真正做左政府工,就明白有幾好 同穩定 安全 唔會怕 中年失業連住屋都有問題"},{"pid":"30ae7d841fcaec4c33c91519b8ccd367ca420bc5","tid":434251,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T11:28:43.000Z","msg":"IT : 未到40中已經炒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eab01dee8428a307528d6fef4568693c98d6d2d","tid":434251,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T11:33:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>IT : 未到40中已經炒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你被炒當時幾多歲"},{"pid":"9caf3f5df6eb6535436b49436d6edab9b6f7f0dc","tid":434251,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T11:35:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>IT : 未到40中已經炒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你被炒當時幾多歲</blockquote><br />\n42"},{"pid":"ce49e2ac884d164ad7092e873d9c588e6436c38b","tid":434251,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T11:44:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>IT : 未到40中已經炒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你被炒當時幾多歲</blockquote><br />\n42</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2426338f88b390cf663e8df7621725f0ba1e5512","tid":434251,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T11:47:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>IT : 未到40中已經炒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你被炒當時幾多歲</blockquote><br />\n42</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做多咗2年唔錯吖，補多啲錢走，使晒未? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}